    "stat_block": {
        "type": "stat_block",
        "subtype": "equipment",
        "text": "This *+1 striking arquebus* is used by caravan guards to nonlethally\u2014though powerfully\u2014deter large game and bandits. When fired, the spark gun deals mental damage and adds the nonlethal trait to the attack. Each *mindlance* also includes a reinforced stock that benefits from any fundamental runes on the firearm. When you critically succeed at an attack roll with a *mindlance*, the target becomes frightened 2 unless it succeeds at a DC 24 Will save.",
        "level": 8,
